latestPosts.caption:
To the year that was a blur—thank you for being one of the best.

To the people who entered my life, old and new—I hope I’m lucky enough to keep you forever. 
To loved ones I lost—friends and my beloved Theo—our memories will remain core. 
To my body—thank you for showing me I’m stronger than I ever thought possible, powering through sleepless nights and pushing past limits.

To my fans, 

Genie is in its final stages! The VFX (it’s a fantasy film, after all) is taking time, and Rahman sir’s magic is still to come. We’re aiming for an early summer release, and I genuinely believe it’ll be worth the wait.

Wayfarer’s film is 73 days in, with 3 weeks left (we even shot through midnight on New Year’s!).

Odum Kuthira is halfway done, and we’re hoping to wrap up immediately after Wayfarer

I hope you all had a great 2024… onwards to the next one ! HAPPY NEW YEAR 🎆

latestPosts.caption:
Heading to Abu Dhabi? Here are my personal top 3 experiences I think you shouldn’t miss: (extra fun when you’ve got your friends with you)

1️⃣ Clymb Indoor Skydiving – Such a fun experience! I wasn’t sooo bad for my first lesson ok? Can’t compare to the instructor who has been doing this for ages🪂
2️⃣ Jet Cars – If you book your slot during sunset it’s even more beautiful to cruise into golden hour. Trust me, it’s as cool as it sounds. 🌅🚗
3️⃣ YAS Waterworld Slides – make sure you give yourself a whole day to both chill and do thrill rides . And pack a towel!! 💦🎢

Trust me. Add these to your list and thank me later 😜
#inabudhabi 
@visitabudhabi @clymbyasisland @jetcarsuae @yaswaterworldyasisland

latestPosts.caption:
Stepping into Abu Dhabi’s rich tapestry of history and culture 🌍✨ From the timeless charm of Qasr Al Hosn, the oldest stone building in the city, to the intricate craftsmanship at the House of Artisans, every corner tells a story. And then there’s the breathtaking majesty of the Sheikh Zayed Grand Mosque, a masterpiece that leaves you in awe. 🕌💫 This journey isn’t just about places, it’s about connecting with a legacy. #CulturalAbuDhabi #HeritageUnveiled #inabudhabi 
@visitabudhabi
